data.description: This charming 3 bed / 2 bath home, full of warmth and comfort, is waiting for you!  Upon entering you are greeted with ample natural light and beautiful hardwood floors in the living room.   From the living room you will see lovely vinyl planking in the kitchen and all appliances have been updated with in the last 2 years.  You will enjoy the spacious hallway between the updated bathroom and 2 bedrooms that also have hard wood floors.  The lower level features a large finished family room and a bedroom with a walk in closet and a bathroom.
